# Quality Gates

**Canonical source:** [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) §9

Before marking work complete:

| Gate | Command |
| --- | --- |
| 1.1 AI audit | vs [`docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md`](../../docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md) |
| 1.2 Lint + typecheck | `npm run lint` · `npm run typecheck` |
| 1.3 Docker smoke | `npm run docker:test:smoke` |

## Agent guardrails

- **Never** auto-commit or auto-push
- **Never** create files outside [`docs/BLUEPRINT.md`](../../docs/BLUEPRINT.md)
- **One batch per PR** — [`docs/ROADMAP.md`](../../docs/ROADMAP.md)
- End-of-batch: Meta-Prompt Evaluation → [`docs/AI_VELOCITY_LOG.md`](../../docs/AI_VELOCITY_LOG.md)

Full workflow and escape hatch: [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) §9.
